sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>ChatbotPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>ChatSendMessageView
    participant Bot as Rule-Based Engine
    participant Model as ChatSession / ChatMessage
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Type security question
    FE->>API: POST /api/chat/send/ {session_id, message}
    API->>DB: ChatSession.objects.get_or_create(user, session_id)
    DB-->>API: ChatSession instance
    API->>DB: ChatMessage.objects.create(session, role="user", content=message)
    API->>Bot: _handle_greeting(message)
    Bot-->>API: Not a greeting
    API->>Bot: _handle_conversation(message)
    Bot->>Bot: _handle_identity(message)
    Bot->>Bot: _handle_joke(message)
    Bot->>Bot: _fallback_free_response(message)
    Bot-->>API: Rule-based response text
    API->>DB: ChatMessage.objects.create(session, role="assistant", content=response)
    DB-->>API: Message saved
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {response, session_id}
    FE-->>U: Display DurianBot response in MessageBubble
